eligibilityModule.eligibilityCriteria:
Inclusion criteria are

1. Male and female aged 18 years or older;
2. Within 3 (day 1 until 4 months post stroke) months after stroke-onset
3. Discharged from the acute care settings

Exclusion criteria are

1. Unable to answer the evaluation questions;
2. Unable to see the graph of the Rehabkompassen®;
3. without BankID.
